<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EduKit </title>
    <style>
        /* --- Reset y Variables Globales --- */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        :root {
            --bg-color: #f9f9fb;
            --card-bg: #ffffff;
            --text-main: #1d1d1f;
            --text-muted: #6e6e73;
            --accent: #0066cc;
            --border-color: #e5e5e7;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            line-height: 1.5;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        /* --- Contenedor Principal --- */
        .container {
            max-width: 1000px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        /* --- Encabezado --- */
        header {
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        header p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* --- Grid de Kits --- */
        .kits-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
            gap: 24px;
        }

        /* --- Tarjeta de Kit (Card) --- */
        .kit-card {
            background-color: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
        }

        .kit-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
        }

        .kit-tag {
            align-self: flex-start;
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
            color: var(--accent);
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .kit-title {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .kit-description {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
            flex-grow: 1;
        }

        /* --- Enlace / Botón Acción --- */
        .kit-link {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
            transition: color 0.2s ease;
        }

        .kit-link:hover {
            color: var(--accent);
        }

        .kit-link span {
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .kit-card:hover .kit-link span {
            transform: translateX(4px);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <header>
            <h1>EduKit</h1>
            <p>Una colección de herramientas, recursos y proyectos prácticos.</p>
        </header>

        <main class="kits-grid">
            <!-- Kit 1 -->
            <article class="kit-card">
                <div>
                    <div class="kit-tag">Desarrollo Web</div>
                    <h2 class="kit-title">Kit de Inicio Frontend</h2>
                    <p class="kit-description">Plantillas limpias en HTML, CSS y configuraciones base para arrancar cualquier interfaz rápidamente.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="index.html" class="kit-">Explorar kit <span>&rarr;</span></a>
            </article>

          
      

          
        </main>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
